ar.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999364834475297, \"rank\": 6.352058328711376e-05, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final, Kerr\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"a British-record time\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"3:27.79\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"the rivalry\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Over the years there has been a bit of back and forth,' Kerr toldEurosportwhen asked to 'spill the tea' about his bitter feud with Ingebrigtsen.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr toldEurosportwhen\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"the tea\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"his bitter feud\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I felt a little bit disrespected last year after my first world title (at the 2023 World Championships in Budapest, Hungary).\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999364834475297, \"rank\": 6.352058328711376e-05, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.8619408158230486, \"rank\": 0.1601651462782807, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first world title\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 World Championships\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is something about someone saying they are not 100 per cent when you go out and get your first world title that makes it sting a bit.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"your first world title\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I want everyone to be at their best and I want to beat everyone at their best.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where it started for me, and I just started being honest with the questions.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the questions\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was asked and instead of giving everyone the benefit of the doubt, I was being myself without much filter.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"the benefit\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"the doubt\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"much filter\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think that annoyed some people and turned some heads.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"some heads\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Running and athletics is a gentleman's sport so there is not a lot of that, but it is what it is.'\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gentleman's sport\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh Kerr spills the tea on his rivalry with Jakob Ingebrigtsen \\u00e2\\u0098\\u0095\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u0080#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/3Bq6C5JBn5 Ingebrigtsen, who said he could beat Kerr blindfolded earlier this year, posted about the Briton on Instagram after Tuesday night's race at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9998357107086292, \"rank\": 0.0001269376875567929, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}, {\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tea\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"his rivalry\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"the Briton\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"Instagram\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday night's race\", \"from\": 1691, \"to